07:04:10.000Z","msg":"第一條片個肥佬係退役橫綱嚟, 傻閪<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Akebono Tarō 曙太郎</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Akebono_Tar%C5%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FAkebono_Tar%25C5%258D&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2WWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=00c0b30b\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Akebono_Tar%C5%8D</a><br />\n嗰場比賽係 May 3, 2006 東京 Hero's 5<br />\nAkebono (當時37歲) VS 摔跤手 Don Frye (當時41歲)<br />\n而 Akebono MMA紀錄係四場全輸<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N0j97J6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN0j97J6.jpg&h=cb964054&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"009ad2101dac67cfeaa17503532d45e95440ea05","tid":2451804,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"21f0bfd3130f38f1b7c6e0d18457c5ec6277c6bf","tid":2451804,"uid":77330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"105455979f75fa23d96b7fe9b5dc1b5ac67c808b","tid":2451804,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a470e6589829bf06d3d7578b96074b139bc983e","tid":2451804,"uid":77330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:52:09.000Z","msg":"有片就唔駛同你口同鼻拗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T05:30:40.000Z","msg":"而家係你單方面鳩噏<br />\n我就貼咗兩條片, 亦有理據同分析<br />\n好多比賽最重個級別係唔限重, 你究竟識唔識? Super Heavyweight 呀<br />\n相撲手可以去打㗎喎, 相撲手咁勁就贏撚咗啦<br />\n<br />\n喂, 中國功夫有發勁添呀, 打撚死啲擂台佬呀<br />\n不過我冇證明"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T06:04:11.000Z","msg":"你咪又係得個鳩噏<br />\n你果兩條片叫相撲手？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:11:59.000Z","msg":"重有邏輯上應該係你搵片去證明你「相撲實贏晒」嘅論點, 唔係我搵片去證明唔係<br />\n同埋搵唔到片即係代表嗰樣嘢唔止擂台上冇作用, 直情連參與嘅勇氣都冇, 而唔係搵唔到片代表嗰樣嘢可能好撚勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇邏輯又冇武術知識又要聲大大, 唔識你就唔好發表偉論吖嘛, 武術post最煩係你呢啲外行人"},{"pid":"d663ab8c400c7bd0c196b6ad8b05531cd15d5dae","tid":2451804,"uid":166766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:29:37.000Z","msg":"實戰講  實力真係好低<br />\n唔同門派都有自己對敵要點<br />\n但睇佢地練上黎就係死練形意   又唔會用實戰去練<br />\n點解mma 選手打到所謂宗師訓低晒就係因為咁<br />\n班所謂中國功夫掌門人就係靠李小龍 同功夫電影呃飯食<br />\n如果迷功夫片去學冇所謂  但要從實戰去學   我唔覺得有邊門功夫係學得過  <br />\n又唔叫人練體能 淨係練架勢<br />\n戰力再高老鼠都唔會打得贏一隻殘弱熊<br />\n自然界其實已經教識人類   要講打之前  先練好體能   <br />\n戰鬥技巧係其次"},{"pid":"387715704eba5f2921c42cb3a7d3b334d5cd306b","tid":2451804,"uid":207050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:33:57.000Z","msg":"不如討論下最好打擊拳擊手好打啲定係最好打嘅軍人好打啲好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efef0c936cd5437a2e1cd78e8a0b58edcc07038","tid":2451804,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"387715704eba5f2921c42cb3a7d3b334d5cd306b","tid":2451804,"uid":207050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:33:57.000Z","msg":"不如討論下最好打擊拳擊手好打啲定係最好打嘅軍人好打啲好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:38:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-NtUUA_3ntw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-NtUUA_3ntw&d=1mBOIAkAA7%2FwaZBThmus2WWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=ec9a2fa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-NtUUA_3ntw</a><br />\n<br />\n依條片解釋左"},{"pid":"6bde4f2fc20f045acaa3586f326aeabf3926d4d8","tid":2451804,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21f0bfd3130f38f1b7c6e0d18457c5ec6277c6bf","tid":2451804,"uid":77330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"105455979f75fa23d96b7fe9b5dc1b5ac67c808b","tid":2451804,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a470e6589829bf06d3d7578b96074b139bc983e","tid":2451804,"uid":77330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:52:09.000Z","msg":"有片就唔駛同你口同鼻拗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T05:30:40.000Z","msg":"而家係你單方面鳩噏<br />\n我就貼咗兩條片, 亦有理據同分析<